@startuml
participant User
box "Cluster" #LightBlue
	participant Frontend
	participant "Cluster mediator"
	participant Subscribers
end box
User -> Frontend: Connect two servers
Frontend -> "Cluster mediator": Connect two servers\nTopic: "subscription"
Frontend -> User: ok
"Cluster mediator" --> Subscribers: Connect
note right: Connects to the specified node only if\n the message is intended for that subscriber
@enduml